    "body": "> Collapse big function into separate component\n\n- [x] `AppProviders` - Contains all custom context providers, also logic to separate providers for each pages\n- [x] `DebugBoxContainer` - Contains configured components that are put inside `DebugBox`\n- [x] `SidebarData` `/browse` - Data for sidebar, separated from `Sidebar` logic\n\n<details>\n  <summary>Changes of plan for `TranslationBar` extraction and it definitely works better</summary>\n\n  - ~~`ArchiveLayoutEdit` `/archive-edit` - Edit extension from `/archive-view` for `ArchiveLayout`~~\n  - ~~`LmdTlBar` `/archive` - Contains component that would appear if screen size is smaller than `md`, moved from `TranslationBar`~~\n  - ~~`MmdTlBar` `/archive` - Contains component that would appear if screen size is larger than `md`, moved from `TranslationBar`~~\n  - ~~`ConfigList` `/archive-edit` - Wrapper of edit exclusive configurations (for screen size larger than `md`), with the child being existing `OverlayProperty` component and related, moved from `TranslationBar`~~\n  - ~~`ConfigToggler` `/archive-edit` - Wrapper of overlays and toggle buttons of edit exclusive configurations (for screen size smaller than `md`), moved from `TranslationBar`~~\n</details>\n\n- ~~`OverlayEdit` `/archive-edit` - Edit extension for `Overlay`~~\n- [x] `OverlayApplier` `/archive-edit` - Context containing `OverlayConnector` and `OverlayBoxliner`, moving out from being hardcoded in `OverlayContext`\n\n> Make a reusable component for duplicates\n\n- [x] `button-input` - button with hover effects, has html input under the hood.",
